{"name":"Dretchling","size":"small","type":"fey","tag":"demon","alignment":"chaotic evil","hitDice":"3","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":1,"otherArmorDesc":"11 (natural armor)","speed":"20","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"18 (4d6 + 4)","speedDesc":"20 ft.","strPoints":"11","dexPoints":"11","conPoints":"12","intPoints":"5","wisPoints":"8","chaPoints":"3","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":60,"cr":"1/4","customCr":"1/4 (50 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The dretch can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The dretch regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the dretch can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the dretch can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The dretch can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the dretch's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the dretch's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the dretch dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The dretchling makes two attacks: one with its bite and one with its claw."},{"name":"Bite","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ +2 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 3 (1d6) piercing damage."},{"name":"Claw","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ +2 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 2 (1d4) slashing damage."},{"name":"Tongue Lash","desc":"_Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +2 to hit, reach 15 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 2 (1d4) slashing damage and the dretchling is pulled 15 feet towards the target."},{"name":"Fetid Cloud (1/Day)","desc":"A 10-foot radius of disgusting green gas extends out from the dretch. The gas spreads around corners, and its area is lightly obscured. It lasts for 1 minute or until a strong wind disperses it. Any creature that starts its turn in that area must succeed on a DC 11 Constitution saving throw or be poisoned until the start of its next turn. While poisoned in this way, the target can take either an action or a bonus action on its turn, not both, and can't take reactions."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[{"name":"acid","note":" (Vulnerable)","type":"v"},{"name":"cold","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"poison","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"poisoned"}],"languages":[{"name":"Abyssal","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}